Relative SSB (SSB relative to zero fishing) over all projection years (a performance metrics function of class PM)

Relative SSB (SSB relative to zero fishing) over all projection years (a performance metrics function of class PM)

LRSSB

Arguments

MSE
An object of class MSE

Format

An object of class PM of length 1.

Value

a matrix with n Management procedures (MSE@nMP) and nsim (MSE@nsim) columns from MSE

Examples

loadABT()
#> ABT-MSE objects loaded
LRSSB(MSE_example)
